t a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" property of the map view displayed in your application."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","role":"symbol","title":"MLNUserLocation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNShape","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","title":"MLNShape","abstract":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" is an abs